    "text": [
        "Dear sir,",
        "My name is Zannatul Firdaus, I live at khilgaon in Dhaka. I am a service holder. Today I am writing this letter to inform you that, your company made a mistake about sending my bill to the wrong address.",
        "To embark with, every month, I receive my telephone bill in the first week, but in the last month, I did not receive my bill. After about 10 days, a person from the neighbouring block gave me the bill saying that it had been delivered to his address.",
        "In addition, after getting my bill copy when I went to pay the bill and it was charged BDT. 500 as fine for being late. I argued a lot but they did not listen and I had to pay the fine.",
        "Moreover, I request you to refund the amount that I had to pay as a fine or adjust it in the next bill because it was not my fault that I was late. If you need any more information from me regarding this matter, please feel free to contact me at my email address.",
        "Hoping for a positive response from your regarding this matter.",
        "With regards,",
        "Zannatul"
    ],
